"користити RS485 репетитора."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:19
msgid ""
"Relay connection diagram. Rated current of the built-in relay contacts: up to 10A 250V AC nebo "
"30 V DC. Direct control of household appliances: 230 V AC or devices below 30 V DC."
msgstr ""
